---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout>
	<main class="app-container pt-36">
		<h1 class="text-6xl pb-2 font-bold">Gear</h1>
	</main>
	<section class="app-container py-12 mb-8">
		<div
			class="prose prose-neutral prose-lg md:prose-xl dark:prose-invert prose-img:rounded-xl prose-figure:text-center prose-img:mx-auto"
		>
			<p>
				This is a collection of the tools, equipment, and software I use for photography, development, and everyday work. Inspired by the gear pages of other creators, this serves as both a personal reference and a resource for anyone curious about what powers my creative process.
			</p>

			<h2>Workspace</h2>

			<h3>Computing</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>MacBook Pro 16" (M3 Max)</li>
				<li>Dell UltraSharp 27" 4K Monitor</li>
				<li>Magic Keyboard</li>
				<li>Magic Trackpad</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Desk Setup</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Autonomous SmartDesk Pro</li>
				<li>Herman Miller Aeron Chair</li>
				<li>BenQ ScreenBar Monitor Light</li>
				<li>Anker USB-C Hub</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Photography</h2>

			<h3>Camera Bodies</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Sony α7R V</li>
				<li>Sony α7 III</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Lenses</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Sony FE 24-70mm f/2.8 GM II</li>
				<li>Sony FE 70-200mm f/2.8 GM OSS II</li>
				<li>Sony FE 16-35mm f/2.8 GM</li>
				<li>Sony FE 85mm f/1.4 GM</li>
				<li>Sony FE 35mm f/1.4 GM</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Accessories</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Peak Design Capture Clip v3</li>
				<li>Peak Design Travel Tripod</li>
				<li>SanDisk Extreme Pro CFexpress Type A Cards</li>
				<li>Sony VG-C4EM Vertical Grip</li>
				<li>DJI RS 3 Pro Gimbal</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Audio</h2>

			<h3>Headphones</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Sony WH-1000XM5</li>
				<li>Apple AirPods Pro (2nd generation)</li>
				<li>Sennheiser HD 660S</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Speakers</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Audioengine A5+ Powered Speakers</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>EDC (Everyday Carry)</h2>

			<h3>Essentials</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>iPhone 15 Pro Max</li>
				<li>Apple Watch Ultra 2</li>
				<li>Ridge Wallet</li>
				<li>AirTag in Nomad Leather Loop</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Travel</h2>

			<h3>Bags</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Peak Design Everyday Backpack 30L</li>
				<li>Peak Design Travel Duffelpack 65L</li>
				<li>Peak Design Everyday Sling 10L</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Accessories</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Peak Design Packing Cubes</li>
				<li>Anker PowerCore 26800 PD</li>
				<li>Anker 100W USB-C Charger</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Software & Services</h2>

			<h3>Development</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Visual Studio Code</li>
				<li>iTerm2 with Oh My Zsh</li>
				<li>GitHub Copilot</li>
				<li>Postman</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Design & Creative</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Adobe Lightroom Classic</li>
				<li>Adobe Photoshop</li>
				<li>Figma</li>
				<li>DaVinci Resolve</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Productivity</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Notion</li>
				<li>Things 3</li>
				<li>1Password</li>
				<li>Obsidian</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Utilities</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Raycast</li>
				<li>CleanShot X</li>
				<li>Rectangle</li>
				<li>Hazel</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
